description: Jimmy's Famous Seafood is known to be a Baltimore landmark know for their seafood since 1974, by founder the late Demetrios "Jimmy" Minadakis. In 2014, his sons inherited the restaurant and decided to share their father legacy by creating Jimmy's Famous Seafood Express. Now they're dishing out some of Baltimore best seafood to the people of Bartow. People of Florida prepare to indulge yourselves with the amazing tastes of Jimmy's Famous Seafood!
name: Jimmy's Famous Seafood Express
